258F%25AE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%2F10150290136519512%2F&d=QLHl5Z7mYCo8Y3dX70CtkAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5cebb081\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/mak-chun-fan/%E5%A3%B9%E9%80%B1%E5%88%8A-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%A4%9C%E8%B8%A9%E5%94%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%98%E9%82%B8-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A/10150290136519512/</a><br />\n<br />\n九年前李克強訪港果陣, 已經講緊政治部復活<br />\n改左名做保安科<br />\n<br />\n有人更加話, 如果有警察調去保安科, 需要再宣誓"},{"pid":"6b8dd7f83d2af9492b7726e5984d58d54ecb620d","tid":316333,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"遲早一國一制<br />\n取消香港政策法<br />\n變成中國一個普通城市"},{"pid":"7214042c52afba13ca61e6c294b729a726a1907e","tid":316333,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"01又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d442f671b4f70e265af47f5d85267f0130f91cc3","tid":316333,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲早一國一制<br />\n取消香港政策法<br />\n變成中國一個普通城市</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔會<br />\n<br />\n中共需要香港做國際金融中心, 洗黑錢<br />\n所以唔會取消一國兩制"},{"pid":"c27146b65fdfe7f594e5cf51a6a332208303041b","tid":316333,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"be71269f9a1239edef4b4ec4b23db0042c5daa39","tid":316333,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:55:31.000Z","msg":"洗鬼<br />\n直接拉人都無人出聲ga 啦"},{"pid":"a7cd04941c226416dbc85e513eed2a23895bda9e","tid":316333,"uid":47352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T20:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府內部參考文件 不對外公開<br />\n呢幾個字係用仿宋體<br />\n好似支那好興用呢個字體<br />\n同埋邊有文件係咁樣寫架<br />\n正常係咁架嘛<br />\n<br />\nrestricted(xx) 限閱文件(乜乜）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c7eb349150766838c8e1390ca4d5